snippet.title: Zeepkist - Early Access Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now!! - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1440670/Zeepkist/
Follow twitter!! - https://twitter.com/ZeepkistGame

Trailer music by Duncan Steven: https://twitter.com/duncsteven

--

Welcome to Zeepkist! 😋🏁🏁

If you like weird physics, soapbox racing, and/or creating your own tracks, then this is the game for you!

🔸 Race against time in singleplayer, or against your friends in up to 4-player splitscreen!
🔸 Create your own zeepkist levels with the integrated level editor!
🔸 Unlock hats and soapboxes in the Early Access adventure map, which has 24 levels to complete!
🔸 Enjoy unlimited Dutchness! With classic Dutch content such as the stroopwafel soapbox and the hat of Dutch Santa!
